Class AgnosticThreadLtException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • leitej.exception.LtException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class AgnosticThreadLtException
extends LtException
    The class AgnosticThreadLtException and its subclasses are a form of LtException that indicates conditions that a reasonable application might want to catch.
    Author:
    Julio Leite
